Dear All,

John Wiley & Sons has just published my new book "Cryptography for Visual 
Basic: A Programmer's Guide to the Microsoft CryptoAPI." Bruce Schneier has 
kindly endorsed it: "This is essential reading for anyone who needs to 
understand Microsoft's CryptoAPI,its strengths and its limitations." The 
book includes open source COM objects with a simple interface to help VB 
programmers use the CryptoAPI.

For the actual code, links, and other information, see 
